r documentados", "Reporte de análisis generado"], "enriched": true}	RUN	Crítica	Backlog	\N	\N	INC-20260321-C7EB	\N	0.4	0.0	2026-03-21 17:51:30.360188+00	\N	\N	[]	2026-03-21 17:51:30.360188+00
