itosamente", "Rendimiento de conexiones validado"], "enriched": true}	RUN	Crítica	Backlog	\N	\N	INC-20260321-C7EB	\N	0.5	0.0	2026-03-21 17:51:30.35635+00	\N	\N	[]	2026-03-21 17:51:30.35635+00
